7, will be hoping to build on a strong year which saw her reach a career-high 27 in the world rankings in March.\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1805, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1610, \"end\": 1617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9999985838336238, \"rank\": 1.4161656136986431e-06, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The British record-holder secured her place in Team GB as she powered to victory in the women's 200m at the UK Athletics Championships earlier this month.\", \"from\": 1809, \"to\": 1963, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1813, \"end\": 1820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9998971482800495, \"rank\": 8.553776412829199e-05, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}, {\"begin\": 1917, \"end\": 1943, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Athletics_Championships\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Athletics Championships\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Athletics_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Athletics_Championships\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her success in a championship record time of 22.18 seconds in cold and wet conditions underlined her return to form after her 100m European Championship gold earlier in June.\", \"from\": 1964, \"to\": 2138, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now the target is to claim the biggest prize of all and become the first British woman to claim Olympic sprint gold in either the 100m or 200m.\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2213, \"end\": 2220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9998971482800495, \"rank\": 8.55377641